{"tid":1204044,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"初獨遊福岡","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T17:20:30.000Z","uid":206975,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8dbb1694d73702c55bd024819040c8d583e3373","tid":1204044,"uid":206975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"第一次自己一個旅行<br />\n但係出發前完全唔開心<br />\n更多既係擔心香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FC3d8az.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFC3d8az.png&h=1f0926d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係飛機上面望落去香港<br />\n我覺得香港好靚<br />\n但係點解呢一刻既香港會咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNSqZhH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNSqZhH.png&h=90aca1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落機之後去食暖慕同family mart既炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RXbGxDp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRXbGxDp.png&h=4c65afe6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zz0PGwT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZz0PGwT.png&h=08eb13bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次住係中洲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3SZdoLA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SZdoLA.png&h=80e8bc5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完就去咗博多亂咁行，行下100円店同其他鋪頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VdNtcv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VdNtcv.png&h=6c2ffacf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QJC6JLT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQJC6JLT.png&h=f2851fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvLToLV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJvLToLV.png&h=d7b1338d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚食今半，鐘意食壽喜燒既應該都會識呢間<br />\n真係好貴，但係真係好好食，一世都唔會忘記個口感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuONtdd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyuONtdd.png&h=a7847e37&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vvhbarA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvvhbarA.png&h=033e940d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽就搭去天神地下街行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yL8cFG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yL8cFG.png&h=4c3a1491&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYPwUT4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYPwUT4.png&h=2b77dfd5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTutcFM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTutcFM.png&h=7404452b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就翻去啦<br />\nDAY1完<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m36OW8A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm36OW8A.png&h=3c058110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"a31e0771c156886dd69d02717f1d9141513aa4a1","tid":1204044,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"小心你本passport捱唔到返黎"},{"pid":"ca10820bac4eee00a8b0355bc04111d976d97fc0","tid":1204044,"uid":33703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}